title: No labels for Annie
creator_contributor_role: Healthsharing Women. Publishing and Production Group, production company

description: A portrait of Annette Duras, a young woman whose life has become enriched and meaningful since obtaining a job in "open employment". The program highlights the need for us to resist categorising others with destructive labels and illustrates the positive effect on people when labels are discarded.
